Package net.paulhertz.aifile

Class FindComponentWithIDVisitor

java.lang.Object
net.paulhertz.aifile.ComponentVisitor
net.paulhertz.aifile.FindComponentWithIDVisitor
public class FindComponentWithIDVisitor
extends ComponentVisitor
Finds a DisplayComponent with specified ID. If the component is found, compIsFound() returns true and the component can be retrieved from getFoundComp(). Typically, you would cache the ID or IDs upon instantiating the component, for later retrieval.
